node.text: Had the best time with the best people! I truly love my friends! Everyone came together for an epic day on the water with @seadoo. There really isn’t enough to say about these folks so I’ll point you to the link in my bio to check out the epic day we had! This header shot of the squad taken by @thechrishau whilst treading water no less. I love it! #thedopesquad #seadoolife #ad

node.text: It feels like we’re in a new era of making content online. It’s exciting stuff, scary stuff, challenging stuff- but that’s the good stuff. Just uploaded a video about it all and new directions on the channel! What are your thoughts? Would love to hear them down below! New video linked in bio. (New presets and website launching soon!)
